      "representation": "view",
      "value": "<div class=\"contentLayout2\"><style>[data-colorid=t418q89haf]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=t418q89haf]{color:#004eb3}[data-colorid=ak8j8uqlk1]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=ak8j8uqlk1]{color:#004eb3}</style>\n<div class=\"columnLayout two-equal\" data-layout=\"two-equal\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<p><strong><span data-colorid=\"t418q89haf\">Project</span></strong>: Dragon Plush</p><p><strong><span data-colorid=\"ak8j8uqlk1\">Scene by</span></strong>: Julia Boisvert, Evan Dickinson,  Emmalie Hall</p></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://downloads.renderman.pixar.com/resources/Dragon_Plush_Maya.zip\" rel=\"nofollow\"><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-right-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-right\" alt=\"DownloadButton2.png\" width=\"158\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/611713025/DownloadButton2.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758627947834&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=158&amp;height=37\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/611713025/DownloadButton2.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758627947834&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"68\" data-width=\"286\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"611713055\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"DownloadButton2.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"611713025\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"86f3312c-15b6-48d0-8571-a70dcb713902\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/611713025/DownloadButton2.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758627947834&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=286&amp;height=68 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/611713025/DownloadButton2.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758627947834&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=158&amp;height=37 1x\" /></span></a><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://downloads.renderman.pixar.com/resources/Dragon_Plush_Houdini.zip\" rel=\"nofollow\"><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-right-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-right\" alt=\"DownloadButton2.png\" width=\"158\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/611713025/DownloadButton2.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758627947834&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=158&amp;height=37\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/611713025/DownloadButton2.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758627947834&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"68\" data-width=\"286\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"611713055\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"DownloadButton2.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"611713025\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"86f3312c-15b6-48d0-8571-a70dcb713902\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/611713025/DownloadButton2.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758627947834&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=286&amp;height=68 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/611713025/DownloadButton2.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758627947834&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=158&amp;height=37 1x\" /></span></a></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout fixed-width\" data-layout=\"fixed-width\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<h2 id=\"DragonPlush-Overview\">Overview</h2><p>Dragon Plush is an asset look developed by artist Julia Boisvert and modeled by Evan Dickinson from a concept by Emmalie Hall for a group short titled <em>Serendipity</em>.</p><p>The multi-layered felt groom was developed in Houdini and rendered using RenderMan and LamaHairChiang shaders. The character consists of a variety of materials and hair types created using a mixture of Substance Painter, Houdini, and RenderMan for Maya.<br /><br />.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"dragon_plush.jpg\" width=\"760\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/611713025/dragon_plush.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758628081914&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=427\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/611713025/dragon_plush.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758628081914&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"1080\" data-width=\"1920\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"611254434\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"dragon_plush.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"611713025\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"9eab068b-7d03-4151-942c-933ecf89f174\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/611713025/dragon_plush.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758628081914&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1520&amp;height=854 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/611713025/dragon_plush.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758628081914&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=427 1x\" /></span><hr /><h3 style=\"text-align: center;\" id=\"DragonPlush-AbouttheArtist\">About the Artist</h3><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://www.artstation.com/lunarly\" rel=\"nofollow\"><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"Julia_Boisvert_Headshot.png\" width=\"200\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/611713025/Julia_Boisvert_Headshot.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758628097499&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=200&amp;height=200\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/611713025/Julia_Boisvert_Headshot.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758628097499&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"512\" data-width=\"512\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"611516552\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"Julia_Boisvert_Headshot.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"611713025\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"f40ae507-eb56-4633-bd06-ffbb48b3a2fc\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/611713025/Julia_Boisvert_Headshot.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758628097499&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=400&amp;height=400 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/611713025/Julia_Boisvert_Headshot.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758628097499&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=200&amp;height=200 1x\" /></span></a><p>Julia Boisvert is a Visualization student at Texas A&amp;M University with interests in look and visual development. She enjoys creating environment-centered 2D art and is currently interested in further exploring character and groom-driven look development.</p><hr /><p>This project is available with an Attribution-NonCommercial 4.0 International License. This allows you to share and redistribute for non-commercial purposes, provided that you credit the original author.</p><div class=\"confluence-information-macro confluence-information-macro-information conf-macro output-block\" data-hasbody=\"true\" data-macro-id=\"8ed14c62-789b-4d41-b943-5821cf4359a2\" data-macro-name=\"info\"><span class=\"aui-icon aui-icon-small aui-iconfont-info confluence-information-macro-icon\"> </span><div class=\"confluence-information-macro-body\"><h3 id=\"DragonPlush-Attribution-NonCommercial4.0International(CCBY-NC4.0)\">Attribution-NonCommercial 4.0 International (CC BY-NC 4.0)</h3></div></div><p /><p /><p /><p /></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>"
